        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "884e",
          "text": "“It is my experience that the world itself has a role to play in our liberation. Its very pressures, pains, and risks can wake us up — release us from the bonds of ego and guide us home to our vast, true nature.”",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
