        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_11",
          "href": null,
          "name": "754e",
          "text": "“The central purpose of the Work that Reconnects is to help people uncover and experience their innate connections with each other and with the systemic, self-healing powers in the web of life, so that they may be enlivened and motivated to play their part in creating a sustainable civilization. In order to do this, we pursue these contributing goals:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5019",
          "text": "to provide people the opportunity to experience and share with others their innermost responses to the present condition of our world",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_13",
          "href": null,
          "name": "d8c1",
          "text": "to reframe their pain for the world as evidence of their interconnectedness in the web of life, and hence of their power to take part in its healing",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8831",
          "text": "to provide people with concepts — from systems science, deep ecology, or spiritual traditions — which illumine this power, along with exercises which reveal its play in their own lives",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "6b9b",
          "text": "to provide methods by which people can experience their interdependence with, their responsibility for life",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "b46e",
          "text": "to connect people with the inspiration they can draw from past and future generations, and other life-forms",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "574a",
          "text": "to enable people to embrace the Great Turning as a challenge which they are fully capable of meeting in a variety of ways, and as a privilege in which they can take joy",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "f0d4",
          "text": "to bring people into mutual support and collaboration in working for the world.”",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4341",
          "text": "— Joanna Macy",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c035",
          "text": "Joanna Macy based The Work that Reconnects on two fundamental assumptions:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 42,
              "href": "http://workthatreconnects.org/the-work-that-reconnects/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 18,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 42,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 18,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_21",
          "href": null,
          "name": "3430",
          "text": "“This world, in which we are born and take our being, is alive. It is not our supply house and sewer; it is our larger body. The intelligence that evolved us from stardust and interconnects us with all beings is sufficient for the healing of our Earth community, if we but align with that purpose.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_22",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ead6",
          "text": "Our true nature is far more ancient and encompassing than the separate self defined by habit and society. We are as intrinsic to our living world as the rivers and trees, woven of the same intricate flows of matter/energy and mind. Having evolved us into self-reflexive consciousness, the world can now know itself through us, behold its own majesty, tell its own stories — and also respond to its own suffering.” (more)",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 419,
              "href": "http://workthatreconnects.org/foundations-of-the-work/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 415,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "34accbc00342_23",
          "href": null,
          "name": "aacf",
          "text": "The four phases of the Work that Reconnects — start with gratitude! (image)",
          "metadata": {
            "id": "1*F5bvUF8FbamOM9u2O88dtw.jpeg",
            "alt": null
          },
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": "INSET_CENTER",
          "markups": [
